content: For some reason I can't progress past level 60. I'm on my 2nd play through and I even used the answer function to see if I was doing something wrong. The correct dialogue ensues, but no message to notify that the level was completed. I believe this to be a glitch.

Love that I can finally cut/paste notes! I also like that in-game websites were used more than in previous games. The voicemails are okay, but I hate the texts since you can't get back to them if you forget to put them in your notes. Overall, another good game!
